name: Punky Hunters
description:
This is the first airdrop for Punky holders!

As we started minting the Punky project, we realized that many people try to snag it in a fraction of a second. This event caused more attention towards the Punkys and more Tezos people came forward to snag them.
We named them shooter or hunter for their unique speed in buying the freshly minted Punkys. These hunters were a great reason for Punkys' performance in sale, and they caused others to join the hunt and challenge their hunting skills!
As the Punky collection is done, we evaluate the people who bought in primary as natural born hunters!

This airdrop is designed to appreciate the people who became primary holders by hunting Punkys in objkt!

This is how we picture you when a Punky is listed!

Rarity tool: 
https://punky.vercel.app
